Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然住宅区域发展得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在稍微远一点的地方  大自然还保留得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气那么好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因为我平日行善的缘故哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿忘记做作业让要同学借你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿第二节课休息就把便当吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小博好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁过分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许的确如博士君所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小要到底是哪一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个香味  是八朔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了哦  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好难受的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃真精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小铃的兴致太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  集合~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己来准备材料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼当然要新鲜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大一条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大收获
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓到了  钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼都不去博士君那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了会分给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的  好像较上劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别钓了  回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有见到那么高兴的麻奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  这里真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说过的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前似乎也是生活在这一带的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所居住的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被包围在森林和自然中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得好像是被关起来了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这名为自然的巨大笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那个…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸当真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是因为要同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是诗歌  诗歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…听起来不像是诗歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才还在这里组装烤肉架来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么只有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现变态  发现变态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始击退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个装扮怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌呀  小博不要这样盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  为什么是泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来烤肉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君  找到小铃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学你来说说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃居然穿泳装…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多  过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没带泳装来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣裤好不容易才干的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得那么好的天气  马上就会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  不用这样道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  做了错事就要好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小博  就以此原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信小铃的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为我会让你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要戏弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  八朔是拿来当点心？还是要烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤？怎么可能做那种遭天谴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭天谴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在八朔上画脸就不会遭天谴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我专用的特别标志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  快盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好饱  好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都吃完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿去称下体重  脸就会发青了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真是美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢烧烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我洗过后再送还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  就这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样博士君的气味就会留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥的玩笑有时很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上小博的衣服和我决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃也够奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自拿我赌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这样道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和博士君在一起我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  小铃钓到了那么大的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而哥哥却一条都没钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是手感不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  连鱼饵的蚯蚓都不敢拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要让小铃来替你上饵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕流个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子也有点晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是发烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还算勉强撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来非得好好道个歉不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  作为赔礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可真无力吐槽了  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病得不轻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去「中心」一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「中心」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「嫦娥医疗中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一家综合性医院  我们都叫它「中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面最新设备一应俱全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家挺有规模的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  还是去看看医生比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就跟你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也能去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小铃你在医院里被传染了感冒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不好办了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  你保护过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟要同学说的一样  好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  来这儿的人也真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是九澄博士对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情  我已经从侄女那儿听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侄女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠她是我的侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听眠说  班上新转来了个奇怪的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇怪的同学」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本人面前说他是「奇怪的同学」  的确有些失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒啊  要不要先验个血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,验血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给你开了些药  回去的时候去药店取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就开始抽血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是方便的话  一起如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是院长栉名田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下贤木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你们生物制药公司的负责人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是境井先生才对啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不过从今以后  就都由在下来接洽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这交接可真突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一些公司内部的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事  没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下手上的这份  姑且就算是敝社的产品介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑且」这话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好像有点缺乏职业作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的  敝社预定今后要加大新药的研发力度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  这或许能够对院长您的研究有所助益
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定不负厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她给你添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈也感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是来取一些常用的药的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常用的药？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  是不是哪里有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心我的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你可真会体贴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  博士君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小铃她  已经吻过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「难不成」  是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  难不成  你对女孩子不感兴趣之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你看啊  虽说是我这个做哥的一面之词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她也确实挺漂亮的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可尽管如此  尽管她对你是那样的穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对她却仍旧是坐怀不乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺奇怪的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这路没走错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么要紧事赶着回去办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微兜了下风而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我是想能够像这样  与你单独相处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不要…  啊…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不行…  你…  住手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:17:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  啊…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她也有说过  你很容易上当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  那孩子来了医院一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那孩子」是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  跟小眠你说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏又是在这个八朔收成不好的年景里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了个那样的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道小眠你也不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是让一诚大哥送你回来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你也太偷奸耍滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也发了烧  去了医院就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真能说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都说什么「去了反而身体会更不好」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  有这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  朝三暮四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早点睡可对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我弄醒的好像就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别大意了  还是吃点药比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  似乎还有那么点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一诚大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四匹狼  嫦娥乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言伤悲  语无常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其形异  人所无
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉神灵  入社坊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那惨红的月光之下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女挥下闪动着妖光的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小镇  白日里处处祥和宁静
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可入了夜  却又似乎有着另一副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  预感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:14.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛しさはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:20.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:33.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君にもう一人きりで待たないでと　言い出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色あせてく　世界の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:46.03,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは終りへ旅をする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:52.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その束の間に　君と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命を削るように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:08.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の向こうに確かにあった　遥かな故郷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君とゆけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:26.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜の向こうに　幻の空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:14.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:20.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:33.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口难开 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:46.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:52.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之间  逢见君影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:08.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:26.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻苍空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,


